title: 11/17/21 DPS Hour 2 Darren Rovell and Rodney Harrison

description:
Darren Rovell talks to Dan about the Staples Center name change. Rovell says the only problem is if Crypto goes in the wrong direction. Rodney Harrison talks to Dan about his big hit on Jerry Rice from his playing days.
